item.title: CVE-2021-20745|2024-08-03T17:53:21.924Z -- takuya%20matsuyama -- inkdrop
item.description: Inkdrop versions prior to v5.3.1 allows an attacker to execute arbitrary OS commands on the system where it runs by loading a file or code snippet containing an invalid iframe into Inkdrop.
